INSTALLATION of SoapsyTools

Tools for SoapSy XML RPC database
Michael Pilgermann
mpilgerm@glam.ac.uk

Content
-------
- Requirements
- Installation
- Uninstall

Requirements
-------------
- SOAPpy
- SoapSy 
- SoapXML RPC by Konstantinos Xynos (kxynos@glam.ac.uk)
- PyXML

Installation
------------
* Unpack the archive
      tar xzvf soapsytools.tar.gz
* Install G4DS as a python site package
    - run the setup module in the g4ds directory with option install (as root):
      python setup.py install


Uninstall
----------
* sorry - you have to delete the site-package directory within your python installation manually for now.
